Name: Vers
Line: Can't sleep.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: There are tabs for that.

Name: Vers
Line: Yeah, but then I'd be sleeping.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Dreams again?

Name: Vers
Line: Wanna fight?

Name: Vers
Line: I slipped.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Right. You slipped as a result of me punching you in the face.

Name: Vers
Line: I was already slipping when you happened to punch me in the face. The two events are not related.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Anything new?

Name: Vers
Line: No.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: You've got to let go of your past.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: It's causing you doubt, and doubt makes you vulnerable.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Control it.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Lose control again and you'll have to convene with the Supreme Intelligence. There is nothing more dangerous to a warrior than emotion.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Humor is a distraction. And anger? Anger only serves the enemy.

Name: Vers
Line: Has anybody seen what the Supreme Intelligence really looks like?

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: No-one can look upon the Supreme Intelligence in its true form. You know that. Our subconscious chooses the way they appear to us. So it's sacred, it's personal. The Kree divulges it ever.

Name: Vers
Line: Who do you see? Your brother?

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: No.

Name: Vers
Line: Father?

Name: Vers
Line: Your old commander?

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Vers...

Name: Vers
Line: (smug)

Name: Vers
Line: (laughing)

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Yes. But you won't succeed in changing my mind on the subject.

Name: Vers
Line: What is the point of giving me these [gestures to her hands] if you don't want me to use them?

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: You're going to use them. The Supreme Intelligence made me the responsibility of showing you how to use them.

Name: Vers
Line: I know how.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Well if that were true, you'd knock me down without them.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Control your impulses. Stop using this [points to her chest, above her heart] and start using this [gestures towards her head]. I need you to be the best version of yourself.

Name: Supreme Intelligence
Line: Vers.

Name: Vers
Line: Intelligence.

Name: Supreme Intelligence
Line: Your commander insists that you're fit to serve.

Name: Vers
Line: I am.

Name: Supreme Intelligence
Line: You struggle with your emotions, with your past which fuels them.

Name: Supreme Intelligence
Line: You are just one victim of the Skrull expansion that has threatened our civilisation for centuries. Imposters who silently infiltrate then take over our planets.

Name: Supreme Intelligence
Line: Horrors which you remember and so much which you do not.

Name: Vers
Line: It's all... blank. My life. You're supposed to take the form of you I most admire but I don't even remember who this person was to me.

Name: Supreme Intelligence
Line: Perhaps this is a mercy, sparing you from a deeper pain. Freeing you to do what all Kree must. Put your people's needs before your own. We've given you a great gift, a chance to fight for the good of all Kree.

Name: Vers
Line: I want to serve.

Name: Supreme Intelligence
Line: Then master yourself; what was given can be taken away.

Name: Vers
Line: I won't let you down.

Name: Supreme Intelligence
Line: We'll know soon enough. You have a mission. Serve well and with honor.

Name: Vers
Line: Why?

Name: Vers
Line: Well maybe if you were more attractive then it would be less disturbing.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Listen up team! Knock it off (pointing at Carol).

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Alright, prepare for a search and rescue of our spy, Soh-Larr. The Skrulls have invaded yet another border planet, this time Torfa. Soh-Larr sent a warning signal, which we've intercepted, that his cover's blown. The Skrull General Talos has sent kill units to find him. Should they reach him before we do, the intelligence he has acquired over three years is as good as theirs. The accusors will bomb a Skrull stronghold here in the south. We slip in, we locate Soh-Larr and we get out, leaving them none the wiser. The Torfa populace; we are not to interfere with them nor them with us. Nothing compromises the security of our mission. Proceed with caution. Follow protocol before extracting him.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: This is a dangerous mission, we must all be ready to join the collective if that is our fate today. For the good of all Kree!

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Vers, track Soh-Larr's beacon. Att-Lass and Minn-Erva find elevation.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Minn-Erva?

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Repeat.

Name: Vers
Line: His beacon's coming from that temple. Let's move.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: No. This is the perfect spot for an ambush. Only one way in, only one way out.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: We don't know if they are locals. Too risky.

Name: Vers
Line: You don't have to go with me. I'll go alone.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: No! You won't.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Right. Keep a close radius, we lose comms we meet back at the Helion. Come on.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Get back!

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Get back. Back!

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Minn-Erva, do you have eyes on this?

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: (to the locals) Get back! Minn-Erva!

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: I don't want to hurt you. Get back! Stay back!

Name: Vers
Line: HGX-78

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Skrulls!

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Vers!

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Back to the Helion!

Name: Vers
Line: How did you know the code?

Name: General Talos (voiceover)
Line: Where are we?

Name: Maria
Line: Where's your head at?

Name: Vers
Line: In the clouds. Where's yours?

Name: Maria
Line: On my shoulders. About to show these boys how to do it. You ready?

Name: Vers
Line: Higher, further, faster baby.

Name: Maria
Line: That's right.

Name: General Talos (voiceover)
Line: This can't be right.

Name: General Talos (voiceover)
Line: Go back even further.

Name: General Talos (voiceover)
Line: Who is this person? Are we in the right...?

Name: General Talos (voiceover)
Line: Am I the only one who's confused here?

Name: Maria
Line: Get your butt's inside, it's time to eat.

Name: Carol
Line: Prepare for takeoff Lieutenant Trouble.

Name: General Talos (voiceover)
Line: Charming memory.

Name: Vers
Line: Early start to your morning.

Name: Vers
Line: Flying airplanes never feels like work.

Name: Vers
Line: I prefer the view from up there.

Name: General Talos (voiceover)
Line: Wait, wait, wait. That's her. Get her back.

Name: Vers
Line: I prefer the view from up there.

Name: General Talos (voiceover)
Line: What's that on her shirt? I couldn't read it.

Name: Vers
Line: I prefer the view from up there.

Name: General Talos (voiceover)
Line: Focus.

Name: Vers
Line: Excuse me?

Name: General Talos (voiceover)
Line: Look down.

Name: General Talos (voiceover)
Line: Focus. Pegasus, Dr. Wendy Lawson. That's her.

Name: Carol
Line: Can you hear that?

Name: General Talos (voiceover)
Line: Do we have the location?

Name: General Talos (voiceover)
Line: Now track Lawson until we find the energy signature.

Name: General Talos (voiceover)
Line: Interesting.

Name: General Talos (voiceover)
Line: Huh. Hold on. Go back right before this. Go back.

Name: Carol
Line: That's no MIG, Lawson.

Name: General Talos (voiceover)
Line: This is it. Now, let me see where you're headed. That's right, look at the coordinates. (Vers begins having flashbacks to directly after the explosion) Focus. (Vers shuts here eyes) Open, please. That's it. That's it. (Vers begins looking at the coordinates, but her vision is fuzzy)You're almost there.You're almost there. (Vers shuts her eyes, squeezing them shut) Don't fight it. (Vers visions about the explosion come back, this time focusing on the fire around the plane) Focus!

Name: General Talos (voiceover)
Line: Get her back. Get her back now!

Name: Vers
Line: What did you do to me?

Name: Vers
Line: What did you put in my head?

Name: Vers
Line: But those aren't my memories.

Name: Vers
Line: Enough of your mind games! What do you want?

Name: Vers
Line: I don't know any Doctor Lawson.

Name: Vers
Line: You wouldn't know how these things come off would ya? No? Fine.

Name: Vers
Line: Hey!

Name: Talos
Line: Leaving so soon? We're just getting to know each other.

Name: Vers
Line: Vers to Star Force Command. Do you read me?

Name: Vers
Line: Hello? Do you copy?

Name: Vers
Line: Hi, I'm Vers. Kree Star Force. Is this C-53? Do you understand me? Is my universal translator working?

Name: Vers
Line: Oh, good. Are you in charge of security for this district?

Name: Vers
Line: Where can I find communications equipment?

Name: Vers
Line: Thank you.

Name: Vers
Line: Come on.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Vers. Verify, CTC39.

Name: Vers
Line: GRX31600, and I'm fine thank you for asking. Is everyone ok, what happened?

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Skrull ambush. I thought we'd lost you. Did you find Soh-Larr?

Name: Vers
Line: It wasn't Soh-Larr. Talos simmed him, even knew his code.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: That's impossible. That code was buried in his unconscious.

Name: Vers
Line: The Skrulls messed with my mind. The machine that they used, I think it was how they extracted Soh-Larr's code.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Vers, where are you?

Name: Vers
Line: I'm on planet C-53. The Skrulls are looking for someone named Lawson.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Who?

Name: Vers
Line: She's... who I see...

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: She's what? Vers. Vers, what?

Name: Vers
Line: She's a scientist. They think that she's cracked the code on light speed tech. I have to get to her before they do, or else they'll be able to invade new galaxies.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: No. You've been caught once already. How far to C-53?

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Vers. Hold your position until we get there, keep your comms online so that we can contact you.

Name: Vers
Line: No! What if they get a hold of it before...

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Vers? Vers!

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: She's stronger than you think.

Name: Fury
Line: Excuse me miss, do you know anything about a lady who went through the roof of that Blockbuster over there? Witness says she was dressed for laser tag.

Name: Vers
Line: Oh. Yeah, I think she went that way.

Name: Fury
Line: Ah. I'd like to ask you some questions. Maybe give you the 4-1-1 on late night drop-bys. Could I see some identification, please?

Name: Vers
Line: Vers. Kree Star Force. We don't carry identification on metal cards.

Name: Fury
Line: Vers. Star Force. How long are you planning on being in town?

Name: Vers
Line: Oh, I'll be out of your hair as soon as I track down the Skrulls which are infiltrating your planet.

Name: Fury
Line: Skrulls?

Name: Vers
Line: Shape-shifters. They can transform into any lifeform down to the DNA. Oh boy, you guys don't have a clue do you?

Name: Fury
Line: Oh, oh, oh, oh. Hold on. How do we know that you're not one of those... shapeshifters?

Name: Vers
Line: Congratulations Agent Fury. You have finally asked a relevant question.

Name: Fury
Line: Oh! Congratulations to you Star Force Lady. You're under arrest.

Name: Fury
Line: Let's greet them at the station.

Name: Fury
Line: You're saying he's not from around here?

Name: Fury
Line: Well, I'd say fine. But it can't believe what it's seeing.

Name: Fury
Line: Talked like him too.

Name: Fury
Line: The word she used was infiltration.

Name: Fury
Line: Not 'till I say this.

Name: Fury
Line: I got to find Blockbuster girl. I got word on a motorcycle thief which fits her description. She can tell us why these lizards are here, maybe she can tell us how to kick them to the curb.

Name: Fury
Line: Yes sir.

Name: Vers
Line: Where was this photograph taken?

Name: Vers
Line: Where's Pegasus?

Name: Fury
Line: That's classified. Not unlike the file I started on you.

Name: Fury
Line: But I see you changed it up a bit since then. Grunge is a good look for you.

Name: Fury
Line: It's cool. You know, space invasion, big car chase, got to watch an alien autopsy. Typical 9 to 5.

Name: Vers
Line: So you saw one?

Name: Fury
Line: I was never one to believe in aliens. But I can't unsee that.

Name: Vers
Line: This is gonna get a little awkward but I gotta ask.

Name: Fury
Line: You think I'm one of those green things.

Name: Vers
Line: Can't be too careful.

Name: Fury
Line: You are looking at 100 percent red-blooded Earthman.

Name: Vers
Line: I'm afraid I'm gonna need proof.

Name: Fury
Line: We talking cheek swab or urine sample.

Name: Carol
Line: No. The DNA would match.

Name: Fury
Line: Well my AOL password.

Name: Vers
Line: Skrulls can only assume recent memories of their host bodies.

Name: Fury
Line: Oh oh! You wanna get personal.

Name: Vers
Line: Where were you born?

Name: Fury
Line: Huntsville, Alabama. But technically I don't remember that part.

Name: Fury
Line: Mr. Snuffers.

Name: Vers
Line: Mr. Snuffers?

Name: Fury
Line: That's what I said. Did I pass?

Name: Vers
Line: Not yet. First job?

Name: Fury
Line: Soldier, straight out of high school. Got the ranks of full breed Colonel.

Name: Vers
Line: And then?

Name: Fury
Line: Spy.

Name: Vers
Line: Where?

Name: Fury
Line: It was the Cold War, we were everywhere. Uh... Belfast, Bucharest, Belgrade, Budapest.

Name: Vers
Line: Now?

Name: Fury
Line: Been riding a desk for the past few years, trying to figure out where our future enemies are coming from. Never occurred to me that they'd be coming from above.

Name: Vers
Line: Name a detail so bizarre a Skrull could never fabricate it.

Name: Fury
Line: If toast is cut diagonally, I can't eat it. You didn't need that did you?

Name: Vers
Line: No. No, I didn't. But I enjoyed it.

Name: Fury
Line: Ok. Your turn. Prove you're not a Skrull.

Name: Fury
Line: And how is that supposed to prove to me that your not a Skrull?

Name: Vers
Line: It's a photon blast.

Name: Fury
Line: And...?

Name: Vers
Line: A Skrull can't do that. So a full-bred colonel turned spy turned SHIELD agent must have pretty high-security clearance. Where's Pegasus?

Name: Fury
Line: So the Skrulls are alien races which infiltrate and overtake alien planets. And you're a Kree, a race of noble warriors.

Name: Vers
Line: Heroes. Noble warrior heroes.

Name: Fury
Line: So um. What do Skrulls want with Dr. Lawson?

Name: Vers
Line: They believe she developed a light speed engine at Pegasus.

Name: Fury
Line: Light speed engine? I've got to admit, that's not the craziest thing I've heard today.

Name: Vers
Line: Well, it's still early.

Name: Fury
Line: And you, what do you want?

Name: Vers
Line: To stop the Skrulls before they become unstoppable.

Name: Fury
Line: And...? Look, war is a universal language. I know a rogue soldier when I see one, you've got a personal stake in this.

Name: Fury
Line: Nicholas Joseph Fury, Agent of SHIELD.

Name: Vers
Line: Nicholas Joseph Fury, you have three names?

Name: Fury
Line: Everybody calls me Fury. Not Nicholas, not Joseph, not Nick. Just Fury.

Name: Vers
Line: What does your mom call you?

Name: Fury
Line: Fury.

Name: Vers
Line: What do you call her?

Name: Fury
Line: Fury.

Name: Vers
Line: What about your kids?

Name: Fury
Line: If I have them, they'll call me Fury.

Name: Fury
Line: Thank you.

Name: Fury
Line: Oh, hold up. You look like somebody's disaffected niece. Put that on.

Name: Vers
Line: What is this? [gesturing towards the logo]

Name: Fury
Line: It's the SHIELD logo.

Name: Vers
Line: Does announcing your identity on clothing help with the covert part of your job.

Name: Fury
Line: Said the space soldier who was wearing a rubber suit.

Name: Fury
Line: Lose the flannel.

Name: Fury
Line: We're agents of SHIELD.

Name: Vers
Line: We're looking for a woman named Lawson.

Name: Fury
Line: A Dr. Wendy Lawson.

Name: Vers
Line: Do you know her?

Name: Vers
Line: Hmm.

Name: Fury
Line: Are you familiar with the phrase "Welcome Wagon"?

Name: Vers
Line: No.

Name: Fury
Line: Well, this ain't it.

Name: Vers
Line: Is that a communicator?

Name: Fury
Line: Yeah. State-of-the-art two-way pager.

Name: Vers
Line: Who are you paging?

Name: Fury
Line: My mom. Don't worry, I didn't mention you.

Name: Fury
Line: After you.

Name: Vers
Line: Impressive.

Name: Fury
Line: Oh. You should see what I can do with a paperclip.

Name: Fury
Line: Hey, there. How are you?

Name: Fury
Line: Oh my goodness. Look at you. Just look at you. Aren't you the cutest little thing.

Name: Fury
Line: Aren't you cute? And what's your name, huh? What's your name? "Goose", cool name for a cool cat.

Name: Vers
Line: Fury.

Name: Fury
Line: (to Goose)

Name: Fury
Line: Oh. Let me get my fingerprint out. Just let me unravel this puppy.

Name: Fury
Line: You sat there and watched me play with tape? When all you had to do was... [Fury imitates Vers shooting the energy]

Name: Vers
Line: I didn't want to steal your thunder.

Name: Vers
Line: Huh. Lawson.

Name: Vers
Line: Ha. Lawson's plan for the light-speed engine. I wonder why they terminated the project.

Name: Fury
Line: Um, maybe because she's cuckoo.

Name: Vers
Line: Kree glyphs?

Name: Fury
Line: Hmm?

Name: Vers
Line: Lawson is not cuckoo. She's Kree.

Name: Fury
Line: Well, she's dead.

Name: Vers
Line: What?

Name: Fury
Line: She crashed the ASIS aircraft during an unauthorized test flight. Took a pilot down with her. That's why security here's so unfriendly. They're covering up a billion dollar mistake. Oh, and your light-speed engine is toast.

Name: Vers
Line: When did this crash happen?

Name: Fury
Line: Six years ago. 1989.

Name: Vers
Line: Who was the pilot?

Name: Fury
Line: Um, most of this thing's redacted but there is a testimonial here from a Maria Rambeau. Last person to see them both alive.

Name: Fury
Line: You OK?

Name: Vers
Line: Mm-hmm.

Name: Fury
Line: Back in a minute.

Name: Vers
Line: I know Lawson was Kree. She was here on C-53 and died in a plane crash. Do you know anything about this?

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: I just discovered a mission report sent from C-53. There's only so much I'm cleared to tell you Vers, but... [looks to see no one is looking] Lawson was an undercover Kree operative named Mar-Vell. She was working on a unique energy core. Experimenting with tech that apparently could help us win the war.

Name: Fury
Line: She's co-operating with the investigation sir.

Name: Vers
Line: Does it say anything about me?

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Anything about you? No, of course not. Why would it?

Name: Vers
Line: I found evidence that I had a life here.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: On C-53?

Name: Vers
Line: Mar-Vell is who I see in the Supreme Intelligence. I knew her. And I knew her as Lawson.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: This sounds like Skrull simulation Vers.

Name: Vers
Line: No its not! 'Cause I remember I was here!

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Stop! Remember your training. Know your enemy. It could be you. Do not let your emotions undermine your judgment.

Name: Fury
Line: She's on sub-level 6. I'll get off on 5, take the stairs in case she runs for it. Do a pincer move, like we did in Havana.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: We're nearing the jump-point. Leave your beacon on so I can find you. We'll get to the bottom of this Vers. Together.

Name: Vers
Line: Ok.

Name: Fury
Line: Vers!... Vers!

Name: Vers
Line: You called them in?

Name: Fury
Line: My bad!

Name: Fury
Line: What?

Name: Vers
Line: Your communicator. You obviously can't be trusted with it.

Name: Fury
Line: Do you know how to fly this thing?

Name: Vers
Line: Uh... we'll see.

Name: Fury
Line: That's a yes or no question.

Name: Vers
Line: Yes.

Name: Fury
Line: That's what I'm talking about!

Name: Fury
Line: We've got a stowaway.

Name: Vers
Line: Hang on Goose.

Name: Fury
Line: Who's a good kitty huh? Huh Goose? Yes, that's right. Who's a good kitty Goose? You're a good kitty.

Name: Vers
Line: See anyone you know? Funny story... I arrived on Hala, near dead, no memory... That was six years ago.

Name: Fury
Line: So you think you're the pilot that went down with Dr Lawson.

Name: Vers
Line: I'm saying that the last person to see them alive can probably tell us.

Name: Fury
Line: Maria Rambeau.

Name: Carol
Line: Mmhmm. So how do we get to Louisianna?

Name: Fury
Line: Due East. Hang a right at Memphis.

Name: Vers
Line: That agent, that stopped the Skrulls from fighting us...

Name: Fury
Line: Coulson. New guy. Guess he doesn't hate me yet.

Name: Vers
Line: Yeah well, give him time.

Name: Fury
Line: I guess he had a feeling, went with his gut against orders. It's a really hard thing to do. That's what keeps us human.

Name: Vers
Line: I get in trouble for that. A lot.

Name: Fury
Line: I see that about you (Vers and Fury laugh about this). Rescuing the guy how sold you out to the Skrulls. I guess that's not standard Kree operating procedure.

Name: Vers
Line: Well, I won't tell your boss if you don't tell mine.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Ronan.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: It was a trap. To lure our operative Vers to talk for her kidnapper.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: By bombing them out of the galaxy. No. We'll handle this.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Lost. They are lost, for now. But we will find them.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Maintain the course for C-53.

Name: Vers
Line: Excuse me, I'm looking for Maria Rambeau.

Name: Monica
Line: Aunty Carol? Mom, it's Aunty Carol! I knew it, everybody said you were dead but we knew they were lying.

Name: Vers
Line: I'm not really who you think I am.

Name: Maria
Line: That is the craziest shit I have ever heard.

Name: Monica
Line: Green-transforming aliens? There's no such thing.

Name: Fury
Line: You're absolutely right, young lady. There is no such thing. 'Cause if there were, we would want to keep that to ourselves. (Fury looks towards Vers accusingly)

Name: Vers
Line: You don't believe me.

Name: Monica
Line: No way. That's so cool.

Name: Fury
Line: Oh, ho. She can do a lot more than just make tea with those hands.

Name: Monica
Line: Like what? Show us.

Name: Monica
Line: I kept all your stuff, I'll go get it.

Name: Fury
Line: Mmm??

Name: Maria
Line: You don't remember anything?

Name: Vers
Line: I see... flashes. Little moments, but I can't tell what's real. If I could just piece together what happened that morning, maybe it'll all make sense?

Name: Maria
Line: You woke me up, banging on my door at dawn. Your usual move. Back then we had to get up so early, the Air Force still wasn't letting women fly combat, so testing Lawson's planes was our only shot at doing something that mattered. And you wanted to race to base, in your old Mustang, and I wasn't about to argue, 'cause I knew my Camaro would dominate. But you cheated, took a shortcut.

Name: Vers
Line: Since when is a shortcut cheating?

Name: Maria
Line: Since it violates the pre-determined rules of engagement.

Name: Vers
Line: I definitely don't remember those.

Name: Maria
Line: Mmm, of course you don't. (both Maria and Vers laugh for a bit) When I got to the hanger, Lawson was agitated, she said 'she had lives to save'. She was trying to take the Aces up herself, but you said...

Name: Vers
Line: 'If there were lives at stake, I would fly the plane.'

Name: Maria
Line: Yup. Big hero moment. The kind of moment we've both been waiting for. The Doc was always unique. That's why I liked her. But, now you're saying she's from another planet.

Name: Vers
Line: I know this must be hard for you.

Name: Maria
Line: What, this part right here? No, no. Know what's hard? Losing my best friend, in a mission so secret they act like it never even happened. Hard... is knowing you were out there somewhere, too damn stubborn to die. And now you come up in here after 6 years... with your super-charged fire-hands and you expect me to call you... I don't even know what... 'Vers'? Is that really who you are now?

Name: Vers
Line: I don't know.

Name: Monica
Line: Come look.

Name: Monica
Line: This is me and you on Halloween.

Name: Monica
Line: I'm Amelia Earhart and you're Janis Joplin. Oh, this is you when you were little, you didn't get along with your parents so Mom said we became your real family.

Name: Monica
Line: This is us on Christmas. I got more...

Name: Monica
Line: Here's another picture of when you were little. And this is how you right after you graduated... (Monica continues to talk, but the words start to mix together).

Name: Monica
Line: Oh wait. I forgot, your jacket. Mom doesn't let me wear it anymore after I spilled ketchup on it.

Name: Maria
Line: That was all that survived the crash. Or so we thought.

Name: Vers
Line: Don't answer that.

Name: Maria
Line: It's just my neighbor.

Name: Vers
Line: They can change into anyone.

Name: Vers
Line: What do you want?

Name: Maria
Line: Hey Tom. This is my friend Carol.

Name: Vers
Line: A closer looksie?

Name: Vers
Line: To see the bird parked out by the road. You're really working overtime to sell this one, aren't you Talos?

Name: Maria
Line: I'm sorry. Tom, this isn't really a good time. I'll come by tomorrow? Okay?

Name: Maria
Line: Okay.

Name: Talos
Line: You know, you really should be kinder to your neighbors. You never know when you're gonna need to borrow some sugar.

Name: Talos
Line: Now, hang on a second, before you go swinging those jazz hands around, making a mess in your friend's house - and... it's a lovely home.

Name: Maria
Line: Oh my God. What the hell?!

Name: Talos
Line: No one's gonna hurt the girl. Just, don't kill me. That would really complicate the situation.

Name: Fury
Line: I'm about five seconds from complicating that wall with some ugly-ass Skrull brains.

Name: Talos
Line: I'm sorry I simmed your boss. But now I stand before you as my true self. Without deception.

Name: Vers
Line: And who is that, out there?

Name: Talos
Line: Okay, that's a fair point. But I'm sure that you understand, I had to take some precautions. I saw you crush 20 of my best men with your hands bound. I just wanna talk.

Name: Vers
Line: Last time we talked, I ended up hanging from my ankles.

Name: Talos
Line: That was before I knew who you were. Before I found what made you different from the others. I have an audio recording from Pegasus, of your voice, from a plane crash six years ago. On a device I believe you call a 'black box'.

Name: Maria
Line: They told me it was destroyed in the crash. How'd you get it?

Name: Talos
Line: Does she not understand? Young lady I have a special skill that kinda allows me to get into places I'm not supposed to be.

Name: Maria
Line: Call me young lady again, and I'm gonna put my foot in a place it's not supposed to be.

Name: Talos
Line: Am I supposed to guess where that is?

Name: Talos
Line: Okay, I get it. We're all a little on edge here. But look, I just need your help decoding some coordinates. If you sit down, you listen to this, I assure you, it'll be worth your while.

Name: Carol
Line: Call your buddy back inside and I'll listen.

Name: Talos
Line: Deal.

Name: Talos
Line: Oh my God! Get that thing away! How'd that get in here?

Name: Vers
Line: The cat? This isn't what you're afraid of, is it?

Name: Talos
Line: That's not a cat. That's a Flerken.

Name: Fury
Line: A Flerken? (Fury laughs)

Name: Monica
Line: Mom?

Name: Monica
Line: Why can't I listen to?

Name: Vers
Line: What's happening?

Name: Fury
Line: It's loading.

Name: Vers
Line: That's no MIG, Lawson. Who the hell are they?

Name: Vers
Line: Yes, ma'am. (Vers pushes a lever forward, causing the plane to speed up. The plane following them als also speeds up to catch them. The dogfight between the two planes continue, with Vers pushing the lever sideways in an effort to escape the other plane) What do they want?

Name: Vers
Line: Here come some G's. (Vers pulls the lever backwards, causing the plane to flip in the air. After the flip, Vers and Lawson are trailing the other plane. However, when Vers fires the other plane fires back). They're firing backward. Hold on! (Vers pushes the lever sideways and the plane tilts into another revolution. However, the plane is hit and the wing bursts into flames. Vers struggles to regain control of the plane, but fails to do so]

Name: Vers
Line: Bail out! Bail out! Bail out! Stay with me Lawson! (Vers ejects the cockpit from the plane, and struggles to regain control. Once Vers has aligned the plane parallel to the ground, the plane crashes into a beach)

Name: Maria
Line: Danvers, do you copy?

Name: Vers
Line: Yeah, I copy. We hit ground.

Name: Maria
Line: Can anyone hear me?

Name: Vers
Line: Yeah. I copy! Doc?

Name: Vers
Line: Your blood... it's blue.

Name: Vers
Line: What? Lawson?

Name: Vers
Line: I would say that your delusional but we just got shot down by a spaceship and your blood is blue.

Name: Vers
Line: Save who? How?

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: We have no interest in hurting you.

Name: Vers
Line: No?! Because all the shooting kinda gave me the wrong impression!

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: The energy core, where is it?

Name: Vers
Line: Pararescue's on the way. You have two minutes until you're surrounded.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Then I see no reason to prolong this conversation.

Name: Vers
Line: No wait. (Vers gestures towards the engine of the plane) You mean that energy core?

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Hold your fire.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: She absorbed its power. She's coming with us.

Name: Vers
Line: He lied to me.

Name: Vers
Line: Everything that I knew was a lie.

Name: Talos
Line: Now you understand.

Name: Vers
Line: What? What do I understand now?

Name: Talos
Line: Yon-Rogg killed Mar-Vell. He killed her. Because she found out that she was on the wrong side of an unjust war.

Name: Vers
Line: No. Your people are terrorists... that kill innocents. I saw the ruins on Torfa.

Name: Talos
Line: Ruins that the Accusers are responsible for. My people lived as refugees on Torfa. Homeless, ever since we resisted Kree rule and they destroyed our planet. Now the handful of us that are left, will be slaughtered next...unless you will help me finish what Mar-Vell started. The coordinates you found, would've powered a lightspeed ship capable of carrying us to safety. A new home, where the Kree can't reach us.

Name: Maria
Line: Lawson always told us that her work at Pegasus wasn't to fight wars, but to end them.

Name: Talos
Line: She wanted you to help us find the core.

Name: Vers
Line: Well, I already destroyed it.

Name: Talos
Line: No, you destroyed the engine. The core that powered it is in a remote location. If you help us decode those coordinates, we can find it.

Name: Vers
Line: You'll use it to destroy us.

Name: Talos
Line: We just want a home. You and I lost everything at the hands of the Kree. Can't you see it now? You're not one of them.

Name: Vers
Line: You don't know me. You have no idea who I am. I don't even know who I am!

Name: Maria
Line: You are Carol Danvers. You are the woman on that black box risking her life to do the right thing. My best friend... who supported me as a mother, and a pilot when no one else did. You're smart and funny, and a huge pain in the ass. And you are the most powerful person I knew, way before you could shoot fire from your fist. You hear me? You hear me?

Name: Talos
Line: I know I don't deserve your trust but you were our only lead. We discovered that your energy signature matched Mar-Vell's core. Now, we know why. If only you knew, the importance of it to me. I just need your help decoding the coordinates to Mar-Vell's lab.

Name: Carol
Line: Those weren't coordinates. They're safe vectors.

Name: Fury
Line: Orbital positioning and velocity.

Name: Maria
Line: You didn't find her lab on Earth, because it's not on Earth.

Name: Carol
Line: That was the location on the day of the crash six years ago. If we track its course, we'll find it, in orbit, right now.

Name: Maria
Line: It's just basic physics.

Name: Talos
Line: In orbit? Was that so difficult to figure out? I mean, you're my science guy, right?

Name: Carol
Line: Yon-Rogg will catch up to you soon. We've got to get the core before he does.

Name: Carol
Line: In what?

Name: Fury
Line: Hmm. Your science guy.

Name: Carol
Line: Well, I could use a co-pilot.

Name: Maria
Line: No. No, I... I can't. I can't leave Monica.

Name: Monica
Line: Why? It's okay. I can stay with grandma and pop-pop.

Name: Maria
Line: There's no way I'm going baby. It's too dangerous.

Name: Monica
Line: Testing brand new aerospace tech is dangerous. Didn't you used to do that?

Name: Maria
Line: Your plan is to leave the atmosphere in a craft not designed for the journey, and you anticipate hostile encounters with a technologically superior foreign enemy. Correct?

Name: Monica
Line: That's what I'm saying. You have to go.

Name: Maria
Line: Monica...

Name: Monica
Line: You have the chance to fly the coolest mission in the history of missions. And you're gonna give it up to sit on the couch and watch Fresh Prince with me? I just think that you should consider the kind of example you're setting for your daughter.

Name: Carol
Line: Your Mom's lucky. When they were handing out kids, they gave her the toughest one. Lieutenant Trouble.

Name: Monica
Line: You remember.

Name: Carol
Line: Is that mine? (Carol looks at the jacket sitting in Monica's lap. However, Carol protests when Monica attempts to hand it over). No, no. You hang onto it until I come back. But there is something that I need your help with. I can't wear these Kree colors anymore, and since you're obviously the only person around here with any sense of style...

Name: Monica
Line: No.

Name: Monica
Line: Uh-uh.

Name: Monica
Line: Definitely not. (Both Carol and Monica laugh)

Name: Carol
Line: Well, since we're on the same team...

Name: Carol
Line: How do I look?

Name: Monica
Line: Fresh.

Name: Carol
Line: What took you so long?

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: I'm fine. Thanks for asking.

Name: Carol
Line: PRY46-B...

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: No, no codes. That system is fallible, as we've learned.

Name: Carol
Line: Okay, then let's do this.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Who do I see when I commune with the Supreme Intelligence?

Name: Carol
Line: The person you most admire and respect, I guess. But you would never tell me who.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: And what is your earliest memory of Hala?

Name: Carol
Line: The transfusion. Blue blood running through my veins.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Whose blood?

Name: Carol
Line: (Carol looks sideways, confused and stumbed) Hmm.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: That's my blood that's coursing through her veins.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: What have you done with her?

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: She knows?

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Ronan, Skrulls have infiltrated C-53. Come at once.

Name: Carol
Line: Passing 500 and climbing.

Name: Talos
Line: You know, you really shouldn't have that thing on your lap.

Name: Fury
Line: Our little alliance with you is tenuous at best. And as long as he continues to freak you out (Fury picks up Goose and shoves him towards Talos' face. Talos jerks backward in his seat) like that, yeah I'm gonna keep giving him all the love and hugs he needs, right?

Name: Maria
Line: Can I ask you something? Do you just turn into anything you want?

Name: Talos
Line: Ah well, I have to see it first.

Name: Maria
Line: Can you all do it?

Name: Talos
Line: Physiologically, yeah. But it takes practice and, um, dare I say it, talent to do it well.

Name: Fury
Line: Can you turn into a cat?

Name: Talos
Line: What's a cat?

Name: Maria
Line: What about a filing cabinet?

Name: Talos
Line: Why would I turn into a filing cabinet?

Name: Fury
Line: A venus fly trap. I'll give you $50 right now if you turn into a venus fly trap.

Name: Carol
Line: Switching engines from Scramjet to fusion. Buckle up, folks.

Name: Fury
Line: Hey. Is this normal, like space turbulence?

Name: Carol
Line: Pretty much.

Name: Carol
Line: Locking in coordinate grid.

Name: Maria
Line: Where is it?

Name: Talos
Line: It's here. It's gotta be here.

Name: Fury
Line: Well, is it in front of all that nothing, or behind it?

Name: Maria
Line: Is that it? The core?

Name: Carol
Line: In her notes, she called it the Tesseract.

Name: Maria
Line: Whoa. What was Lawson doing with all this kid stuff?

Name: Maria
Line: We're not alone.

Name: Carol
Line: He didn't come here for the Tesseract.

Name: Talos
Line: You did the right thing.

Name: Talos
Line: It's okay, it's okay. She's alright. She's a friend.

Name: Carol
Line: I'm not gonna hurt you.

Name: Talos
Line: She led me to you.

Name: Carol
Line: I'm so sorry. I didn't know.

Name: Talos
Line: Carol, this is war. My hands are filthy from it too. But we're here now. You found my family. This is just the beginning. There's thousands of us separated from each other... scattered throughout the galaxy.

Name: Fury
Line: If I played the same pinball machine for six years I'd have some high scores too.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Fraternizing with the enemy?

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: What did you do to your uniform?

Name: Talos
Line: You can see they're not soldiers, let them go. You can have me.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: And the core?

Name: Carol
Line: You lied to me.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: I made you a better version of yourself. What's given can be taken away.

Name: Supreme Intelligence
Line: There she is. Seems like you time on C-53 jogged the old memory. This jacket? It's killer by the way.

Name: Supreme Intelligence
Line: The music, it's a nice touch.

Name: Carol
Line: Let... me... out.

Name: Supreme Intelligence
Line: No can do.

Name: Carol
Line: If you hurt them, I will burn you to the ground.

Name: Supreme Intelligence
Line: With what exactly? Your powers came from us.

Name: Carol
Line: You didn't give me these powers. The blast did.

Name: Supreme Intelligence
Line: And yet, you've never had the strength to control them on your own.

Name: Fury
Line: It's a cat. Not Hannibal Lecter.

Name: Fury
Line: That thing is clearly busted.

Name: Supreme Intelligence
Line: You did good, ace. Thanks to you, those insidious shapeshifters will threaten our borders no more.

Name: Carol
Line: I used to believe your lies. But the Skrulls are just fighting for a home. You're talking about destroying them because they won't submit to your rule. And neither will I.

Name: Supreme Intelligence
Line: We found you. We embraced you as our own.

Name: Carol
Line: You stole me. From my home, my family, my friends.

Name: Supreme Intelligence
Line: It's cute how hard you try. Remember... without us...you're weak. (Carol pushes herself behind the wall, and sees a screen of her younger memories on Earth playing) You're flawed. Helpless. We saved you.

Name: Supreme Intelligence
Line: Without us... you're only human.

Name: Carol
Line: You're right. I'm only human.

Name: Supreme Intelligence
Line: On Hala, you were reborn. Vers.

Name: Carol
Line: My name... is Carol.

Name: Carol
Line: I've been fighting with one arm tied behind my back. But what happens... (Carol pulls out the chip attached to her neck, causing the energy from her fists to spread to cover her entire body) ...when I'm finally set free?

Name: Fury
Line: You know you're glowing, right?

Name: Carol
Line: I'll explain it later. (Carol opens the lunchbox to reveal the Tesseract glowing inside) Take the Tesseract, leaving the lunchbox.

Name: Fury
Line: (Fury has just unbuckled Goose's collar and is now holding her) Me?

Name: Carol
Line: Yes.

Name: Fury
Line: I'm not touching that thing.

Name: Carol
Line: Want me to get you an oven mitt?

Name: Carol
Line: Get the Skrulls in the QuadJet and go. Take the Flerken with you.

Name: Maria
Line: What about you?

Name: Carol
Line: I'll buy you some time!

Name: Fury
Line: I'm picking you up now. I'm trusting you not to eat me.

Name: Carol
Line: Hey Guys. Arm-wrestle for the Tesseract.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: I used to find you amusing. Let's put an end to this!

Name: Maria
Line: Okay.

Name: Fury
Line: Good kitty.

Name: Carol
Line: You knew all along. Is that why we never hung out?

Name: Carol
Line: Okay.

Name: Fury
Line: Now! Come on! Do your thing. Come on! Dammit, Goose. Pick a side.

Name: Talos
Line: Play it cool. Just like Havana. Do you have the thing?

Name: Fury
Line: Flerken kitty ate it.

Name: Talos
Line: Follow my lead. Cover her eyes. (to Soren)

Name: Talos
Line: Get on the ship. Let's go, let's go.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Nice diversion.

Name: Carol
Line: I could've swore, I put it in there.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: Minn-Erva, take them down on a dropship.

Name: Fury
Line: You all right, friend?

Name: Talos
Line: Never... better.

Name: Maria
Line: We've got a bogey. Coming in hot.

Name: Fury
Line: Ha ha!

Name: Maria
Line: Yes! Boom!

Name: Fury
Line: What the hell was that?

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: I'm so proud of you. You've come a long way since I found you that day by the lake. But can you keep your emotions in check long enough to take me on? Or will it get the better of you, as always? I always told you... you'll be ready, the day you can knock me down as yourself. This is that moment. This is that moment, Vers! Turn off the light show, and prove, prove to me, you can beat me without...

Name: Carol
Line: I have nothing to prove to you.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: I can't go back empty-handed.

Name: Carol
Line: You won't be empty-handed. I'm sending you with a message. Tell the Supreme Intelligence that I'm coming to end it. The war, the lies, all of it.

Name: Yon-Rogg
Line: You can't do this.

Name: Fury
Line: That was a close call, huh, Goosey? Huh? The bad guy's still in there somewhere- [Goose scratches Nick Fury's eye] Oh! MOTHER FLERKEN!!!

Name: Maria
Line: You okay?

Name: Fury
Line: Yeah. It's just a scratch. [a serious scratch is shown on his left eye]

Name: Talos
Line: No...

Name: Carol
Line: I can't believe you got into the raddest dogfight ever.

Name: Maria
Line: I'd say you arrived just in time.

Name: Fury
Line: That's some nifty flying you did out there. SHIELD could always use a good pilot like you.

Name: Maria
Line: I'll consider it. As long as you don't call my flying nifty again. How's your eye?

Name: Fury
Line: Getting better every second.

Name: Carol
Line: Just so I'm clear, you were Soh-Larr, and the SHIELD agent?

Name: Fury
Line: Keller. Tied my boss up, stole his identity.

Name: Talos
Line: I borrowed his likeness. I'm no thief.

Name: Talos
Line: Whose side are you on?

Name: Fury
Line: You're good to go here til you recover, but you and your family will need a new look.

Name: Talos
Line: I could go back to being your boss.

Name: Fury
Line: Please don't.

Name: Talos
Line: Come on. I love sporting his beautiful blue eyes.

Name: Monica
Line: No way, you guys have the best eyes. Don't ever change your eyes.

Name: Carol
Line: I'll help you find a home. Finish what Mar-Vell started.

Name: Monica
Line: They can stay here with us, can't they, Mom?

Name: Maria
Line: They won't be safe here, baby. Auntie Carol is right. They need their own home.

Name: Carol
Line: I'll be back before you know it.

Name: Monica
Line: Maybe I can fly up and meet you halfway.

Name: Fury
Line: Only if you learn to glow, like your Auntie Carol.

Name: Monica
Line: Or maybe I'll build a spaceship. You don't know.

Name: Carol
Line: He doesn't.

Name: Carol
Line: Keep the Tesseract on Earth. Hidden.

Name: Fury
Line: You're sure that's what Marvel would want?

Name: Carol
Line: Mar-Vell.

Name: Fury
Line: That's what I said.

Name: Carol
Line: It's two words. Mar-Vell.

Name: Fury
Line: Mar-Vell. Marvel sounds a lot better. You know, like the Marvelettes? [Singing] 𝅘𝅥𝅮 Oh, yeah, wait a minute Mr. Postman. Ay, ay, ay, ay, Mr. Postman. 𝅘𝅥𝅮 Not ringing any bells?

Name: Carol
Line: Keep singing. Maybe it'll come back to me.

Name: Carol
Line: I upgraded it. Range should be, a couple galaxies, at least.

Name: Fury
Line: What? You think I'm gonna crank call you?

Name: Carol
Line: For emergencies only. Okay?

Name: Fury
Line: Well, if you're ever passing back through this galaxy, be sure to give a brother a shout.

Name: Monica
Line: We got the ketchup stain off.

Name: Carol
Line: Thanks, Lieutenant Trouble. It's hard for me to say goodbye, too.

Name: Maria
Line: Go on.

Name: Fury
Line: I'll neither confirm nor deny the facts of that story.

Name: Fury
Line: I'm sure it will turn up somewhere.

Name: Fury
Line: Then what?

Name: Fury
Line: We have no idea what other intergalactic threats are out there. And our one-woman security force had a prior commitment on the other side of the universe. SHIELD alone can't protect us. We need to find more.

Name: Fury
Line: More heroes.

Name: Fury
Line: We found her and we weren't even looking.

Name: Carol
Line: Where's Fury?
